profile:
Rozon Enterprise has built its reputation on the motto “Quality workmanship carried out with pride and honesty!” Based in Casselman, Ontario since 2009 and founded by Mathieu Rozon, Rozon Enterprise has served and satisfied many clients locally and widespread across Eastern Ontario with their products and services.
The dream started with a strong knowledge and comprehension of the trade accompanied with will, passion and determination. The drive and perseverance that started a small company with a truck, some tools and few hard-working men has now thrived to become a dignitary of the trade. Today, Rozon Enterprise has a fleet of trucks and trailers with multiple employees from labourers to office staff members to better serve all of its clients' needs!
services:
24h Estimates (Mon - Fri)
General Contractor
Roofing Specialist
Residential
Commercial
Agricultural
